commit.message:
toplev.c (rest_of_compilation): Don't optimize the CFG when rebuilding, just before dbr.

        * toplev.c (rest_of_compilation): Don't optimize the CFG
        when rebuilding, just before dbr.

From-SVN: r30330

+	* toplev.c (rest_of_compilation): Don't optimize the CFG
+	when rebuilding, just before dbr.
